OL,5,G2100 The Chase Around the World
OL,6,     FThe teams land in Barcelona to
OL,7,     Ftake on the Vixen and the Menace,
OL,8,     Fwho have set a series of quiz
OL,9,     Fquestions that the teams must
OL,10,     Fsolve to navigate across the city
OL,11,     Fand find Bradley Walsh at the
OL,12,     Ffinish line. Competition is fierce
OL,13,     Fas teams do not want to finish
OL,14,     Flast. If they do they face a
OL,15,     Fhead-to-head showdown with the
OL,16,     FChasers. The final pair will need
OL,17,     Fto beat them to join the other
OL,18,     Fteams and head onto the next city.
OL,19,     FLose and it's the first flight
